"{\"uid\": \"freshplaza.com-north-america-article-9619708-be-part-of-the-olympic-journey-of-dutch-importer\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Sign up for our daily Newsletter and stay up to date with all the latest news!\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 78, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You are receiving this pop-up because this is the first time you are visiting our site.\", \"from\": 80, \"to\": 167, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you keep getting this message, please enable cookies in your browser.\", \"from\": 168, \"to\": 240, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You are using software which is blocking our advertisements (adblocker).\", \"from\": 242, \"to\": 314, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As we provide the news for free, we are relying on revenues from our banners.\", \"from\": 316, \"to\": 393, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So please disable your adblocker and reload the page to continue using this site.Thanks!\", \"from\": 394, \"to\": 482, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Click here for a guide on disabling your adblocker.\", \"from\": 484, \"to\": 535, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sign up for our daily Newsletter and stay up to date with all the latest news!\", \"from\": 537, \"to\": 615, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You are receiving this pop-up because this is the first time you are visiting our site.\", \"from\": 617, \"to\": 704, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you keep getting this message, please enable cookies in your browser.\", \"from\": 705, \"to\": 777, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympic Fruit launches its new campaign today with a brand-new website and brand movie: \\\"Be part of the Olympic Journey.\\\"\", \"from\": 779, \"to\": 900, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 891, \"end\": 898, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dodge_Journey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0025604825861904e-14, \"text\": \"Journey\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dodge_Journey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dodge_Journey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Partners and customers are invited on the Olympic Fruit Journey, both literally and metaphorically.\", \"from\": 901, \"to\": 1000, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 957, \"end\": 964, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dodge_Journey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0025604825861904e-14, \"text\": \"Journey\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dodge_Journey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dodge_Journey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The campaign is another step in the re-positioning of Olympic Fruit.\", \"from\": 1004, \"to\": 1072, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Desmond Jas, Head of Olympic Fruit: \\\"Two years ago, we embarked on a new journey for Olympic Fruit.\", \"from\": 1073, \"to\": 1172, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Our recent focus has been on our internal transformation process.\", \"from\": 1173, \"to\": 1238, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are now ready to take our partners and customers with us on this journey in a truly active way as well.\\\"\", \"from\": 1239, \"to\": 1346, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The launch includes a brand-new website, which also features the new brand movie.\", \"from\": 1348, \"to\": 1429, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There were many reasons to renew and rebrand our website.\", \"from\": 1430, \"to\": 1488, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One of the main goals was to be able to share not only what we do as Olympic Fruit, but more importantly, why we do it.\\\"\", \"from\": 1489, \"to\": 1609, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In fact, the \\\"why\\\" is particularly important to Olympic Fruit.\", \"from\": 1611, \"to\": 1673, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We used Simon Sinek's Golden Circle Model to shape our new positioning.\", \"from\": 1674, \"to\": 1746, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1683, \"end\": 1694, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simon_Sinek\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simon Sinek\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simon_Sinek\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simon_Sinek\"}, {\"begin\": 1697, \"end\": 1710, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Knights_of_the_Golden_Circle\", \"score\": 0.9991642939992228, \"rank\": 0.0007723954555820134, \"text\": \"Golden Circle\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Knights_of_the_Golden_Circle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Knights_of_the_Golden_Circle\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Importing and exporting fruit is what we do.\", \"from\": 1747, \"to\": 1791, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Discovering the endless possibilities in fruit to build colourful and meaningful relationships for generations to come is why we do it,\\\" Jas explains.\", \"from\": 1792, \"to\": 1942, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Be part of the Olympic Journey\\\" is the title of the campaign with which Olympic Fruit intends to engage its partners and customers in 2024.\", \"from\": 1944, \"to\": 2084, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In 2024, we are going to invite and challenge our customers and partners to go on a journey with us, both literally and metaphorically.\", \"from\": 2085, \"to\": 2221, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You will hear more about this very soon!\\\"\", \"from\": 2222, \"to\": 2263, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For more information:Desmond JasOlympic Fruitwww.olympicfruit.com  FreshPublishers \\u00a9 2005-2025 FreshPlaza.com\", \"from\": 2267, \"to\": 2376, \"entities\": []}]}"